# Ollama Modelfile — alias nomic-embed-text as text-embedding-3-small
# Required because cognee uses tiktoken internally which crashes on
# non-OpenAI model names (see pitfall 14)
#
# Usage:
#   ollama create text-embedding-3-small -f Modelfile.embed
#
# This creates an Ollama model called "text-embedding-3-small" that is
# actually nomic-embed-text (768 dimensions). cognee's tiktoken recognizes
# the OpenAI name, and Ollama serves the actual local model.

FROM nomic-embed-text